name: Bookmarks Toolbar - Steel89 Style - Full Version
description:
New Firefox Bookmarks Toolbar style.
Full Version: folder icons are replaced by arrows and the bookmark text is hidden for the sites with favicons.

- Get the Lite version here: http://userstyles.org/styles/23654

Tested on Firefox 3.5
Should work on the other versions too.
